data.description: OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY 11-18-2023  - 1:15 PM   to 3:00  753 20TH AVE., CLARKSTON Very nice, updated home with NEW CARPET throughout! River and canyon views, located at the end of a cul-de-sac in a desirable neighborhood. Large fenced in backyard and garden shed with water spicket for the huge garden area in a private enclosed setting. Attached oversized garage with a covered deck to match. Granite countertops in the kitchen with newer appliance including a dual range/oven either gas or electricity and deck off the kitchen to entertain your friends and /or family. New Carpet.  New gutters around the entire house and vinyl fence on south side of property.
